				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "```smalltalk\n\"Do-it: introduce WowCodebaseLocator and make WowDitaBuild\n ask it for the DITA paths instead of assuming a repo layout.\"\n\n| locatorClass buildClass builderClass |\n\n\"--- Codebase locator for WOW ---\"\nlocatorClass := Smalltalk at: #WowCodebaseLocator ifAbsent: [\n\tObject subclass: #WowCodebaseLocator\n\t\tinstanceVariableNames: ''\n\t\tclassVariableNames: ''\n\t\tpackage: 'Wow-Infra' ].\n\nlocatorClass class\n\tcompile:\n'wowDitaProjectDir\n\t\"Return the root directory of the WOW DITA project.\n\t Initial stub implementation.\n\t The codebase-locator agent is expected to refine this\n\t (e.g., by using git roots / workspace config).\"\n\n\t^ FileLocator home / ''workspace/wow/dita'''\n\tclassified: 'paths'.\n\nlocatorClass class\n\tcompile:\n'wowPositionPaperDitamap\n\t\"Location of the main DITA map for the WOW position paper.\"\n\n\t^ self wowDitaProjectDir / ''src/dita/wow-position.ditamap'''\n\tclassified: 'paths'.\n\n\n\"--- External process runner ---\"\nbuilderClass := Smalltalk at: #GtExternalProcessBuilder ifAbsent: [\n\t^ self error: 'GtExternalProcessBuilder (gtoolkit-external-process) not available in this image' ].\n\n\n\"--- WOW DITA build helper ---\"\nbuildClass := Smalltalk at: #WowDitaBuild ifAbsent: [\n\tObject subclass: #WowDitaBuild\n\t\tinstanceVariableNames: ''\n\t\tclassVariableNames: ''\n\t\tpackage: 'Wow-Tag' ].\n\nbuildClass class\n\tcompile:\n'buildPositionPaperPdf\n\t\"Build the WOW position paper PDF with DITA-OT.\n\t Paths come from WowCodebaseLocator; process execution from\n\t gtoolkit-external-process.\"\n\n\t| workingDir inputMap outputDir builder output |\n\n\tworkingDir := WowCodebaseLocator wowDitaProjectDir.\n\tinputMap := WowCodebaseLocator wowPositionPaperDitamap.\n\toutputDir := workingDir / ''build/pdf''.\n\toutputDir ensureCreateDirectory.\n\n\tbuilder := ', builderClass name ,' new.\n\toutput := builder\n\t\tcommand: ''dita'';\n\t\targ: ''-i'';\n\t\targ: inputMap fullName;\n\t\targ: ''-f'';\n\t\targ: ''pdf'';\n\t\targ: ''-o'';\n\t\targ: outputDir fullName;\n\t\toutput.\n\n\t^ output'\n\tclassified: 'building'.\n```\n\nCall it from a Playground like:\n\n```smalltalk\nWowDitaBuild buildPositionPaperPdf\n```\n\nNow all layout knowledge lives in `WowCodebaseLocator` (where the codebase-locator agent can later replace the stub `wowDitaProjectDir` / `wowPositionPaperDitamap` with a proper git-root or workspace-aware implementation).\n"
